"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-2024-05-07-camille-herron-eyeing-mens-world-record-ultramarathon\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Camille Herron has to believe it is possible.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camille_Herron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Camille Herron\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camille_Herron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camille_Herron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An ultrarunner, Herron is no stranger to breaking records at long distances.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Herron\", \"from\": 63, \"to\": 69}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking records\", \"from\": 88, \"to\": 104}, {\"ngram\": \"long distances\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most recently, she ran 560.33 miles over six days to set the all-time women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s mark.\\u00c2 Now she has another record in her sights: the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s.\\u00c2 Herron, who hasbroken several recordsthroughout her running career, is still basking in her achievements from Lululemon\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s FURTHER six-day ultramarathon that took place in March, where she set 12 world records.\", \"from\": 124, \"to\": 480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"six days\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 173}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-time women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s mark\", \"from\": 181, \"to\": 208}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 210}, {\"ngram\": \"another record\", \"from\": 223, \"to\": 237}, {\"ngram\": \"her sights\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 251}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 253, \"to\": 264}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Herron\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 273}, {\"ngram\": \"her running career\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 333}, {\"ngram\": \"her achievements\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 371}, {\"ngram\": \"six-day ultramarathon\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 420}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 445}, {\"ngram\": \"12 world records\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was one of 10 women from around the world who participated in the sanctioned race that saw 2,880 miles run over the six days in total.\\u00c2 Herron\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s top mark ousted the women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s world record held since 1990\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094549.06 miles run by Sandra Barwick of New Zealand\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094an accomplishment Herron calls a \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cdream come true.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d She also became the first woman to run 500 miles in under five days and set the three-, four-, five- and six-day records among her accomplishments.\\u00c2 No caption needed.\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 714, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandy_Barwick\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sandra Barwick\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandy_Barwick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandy_Barwick\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"10 women\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 526}, {\"ngram\": \"the sanctioned race\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"the six days\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"total\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Herron\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s top mark\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 640}, {\"ngram\": \"the women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s world record\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"1990\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094549.06 miles\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"New Zealand\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094an accomplishment\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 762}, {\"ngram\": \"Herron\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cdream come\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"the first woman\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 832}, {\"ngram\": \"500 miles\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"under five days\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 868}, {\"ngram\": \"the three-, four-, five- and six-day records\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"her accomplishments\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 947}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"No caption\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"@runcamille#lululemonFURTHERpic.twitter.com/zsSG9Eyace Though Herron fell short of the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s six-day record of 644.2 miles, set in 2005 by Yiannis Kouros of Greece, she found herself on track for that record in the early days of the race.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1112, \"end\": 1126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiannis_Kouros\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yiannis Kouros\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiannis_Kouros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiannis_Kouros\"}, {\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\", \"score\": 0.7772999702183332, \"rank\": 0.2864918298103245, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"@runcamille#lululemonFURTHERpic.twitter.com\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"Herron\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s six-day record\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"644.2 miles\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1094}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"that record\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1179}, {\"ngram\": \"the early days\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Through that stretch and beyond, Herron described how the pain she endured ultimately caught up to her.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI knew I could do it, so I stayed very positive and happy, even when internally I was in so much pain,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Herron says.\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that stretch\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"Herron\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1251}, {\"ngram\": \"the pain\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1274}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"so much pain\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"Herron\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy organs were losing control between my bladder and bowels, and there wasn't anything we could do.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy organs\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"my bladder\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1491}, {\"ngram\": \"bowels\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World records break you in every way.\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"World records\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"every way\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have to accept and endure it!\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1614, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I guess I had the best poker face to conceal the amount of pain I was in.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 It was important forHerron to participate in FURTHER, a race that put women first and was unique in its mission.\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best poker\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"the amount\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1678}, {\"ngram\": \"important forHerron\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"its mission\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Citing that just 4\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009313% of sports research studies are reported to be female-focused, FURTHER puts women at the forefront.\\u00c2 Lululemon partnered with the Canadian Sport Institute Pacific in the planning and running of the event.\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 2036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1933, \"end\": 1942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lululemon\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\"}, {\"begin\": 1962, \"end\": 1970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9962071046486276, \"rank\": 0.0033459611841863152, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 1987, \"end\": 1994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Ocean\", \"score\": 0.9867757282375003, \"rank\": 0.013321233781682745, \"text\": \"Pacific\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Ocean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Ocean\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just 4\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009313%\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1831}, {\"ngram\": \"sports research studies\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1858}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"the forefront\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"the planning\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2009}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Various metrics were monitored throughout the six days, many of which were tracked through a tent the participants ran through on each 2.55-mile lap.\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Various metrics\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"the six days\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"a tent\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2134}, {\"ngram\": \"the participants\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"each 2.55-mile lap\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The results, which are slated to be released this fall, will help the brand craft its product for optimal results among women and better understand female performance.\\u00c2 Herron and the race\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s participants trained for over a year with the CSI Pacific staff to best optimize their performance, from pace to caloric intake and gear choices.\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2427, \"end\": 2430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Forensic_science\", \"score\": 0.9786650515565409, \"rank\": 0.02180003667968403, \"text\": \"CSI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Forensic_science\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Forensic_science\"}, {\"begin\": 2431, \"end\": 2438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Ocean\", \"score\": 0.9867757282375003, \"rank\": 0.013321233781682745, \"text\": \"Pacific\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Ocean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Ocean\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The results\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2198}, {\"ngram\": \"the brand\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"its product\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2280}, {\"ngram\": \"optimal results\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"female performance\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2353}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Herron\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s participants\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2392}, {\"ngram\": \"over a year\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"their performance\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2478}, {\"ngram\": \"pace\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2489}, {\"ngram\": \"caloric intake and gear choices\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the race, the runners\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 gear was modified as their bodies changed, accommodating for swelling and varying weather elements.\\u00c2 Herron fully acknowledges that FURTHER\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s conditions in La Quinta, Calif., were difficult.\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2718, \"end\": 2727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Quinta,_California\", \"score\": 0.9775853125629038, \"rank\": 0.017926003126630737, \"text\": \"La Quinta\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Quinta,_California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Quinta,_California\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"the runners\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 gear\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2563}, {\"ngram\": \"their bodies\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2592}, {\"ngram\": \"swelling and varying weather elements\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Herron\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2666}, {\"ngram\": \"FURTHER\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s conditions\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2713}, {\"ngram\": \"Calif.\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ranging from extreme heat, rain and wind storms, it was a challenging environment for Herron to maximize her output to the extent of her ultimate goal in conquering the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s six-day world record.\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"extreme heat, rain and wind storms\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2800}, {\"ngram\": \"a challenging environment\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2834}, {\"ngram\": \"Herron\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 2845}, {\"ngram\": \"her output\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2868}, {\"ngram\": \"the extent\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2882}, {\"ngram\": \"her ultimate goal\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2903}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s six-day world record\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe course was mostly dirt and gravel and felt like a six-day cross country race with a science experiment,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Herron said.\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 3079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe course\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 2966}, {\"ngram\": \"dirt\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 2982}, {\"ngram\": \"a six-day cross country race\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3036}, {\"ngram\": \"a science experiment\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3062}, {\"ngram\": \"Herron\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt was an atypical race and made it more challenging to put up the big numbers.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 Building from that experience, Herron better understands what it will take to have her name atop the six-day record book.\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3085}, {\"ngram\": \"an atypical race\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3106}, {\"ngram\": \"the big numbers.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 Building\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3175}, {\"ngram\": \"that experience\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3196}, {\"ngram\": \"Herron\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3204}, {\"ngram\": \"her name\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3258}, {\"ngram\": \"the six-day record book\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She knows beneficial conditions, optimized nutrition, mental preparation and high-performing gear all will be key in her mission.\\u00c2 But when it comes to Herron\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s reason for wanting the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s record, she reflects on the support felt around her and is inspired by the future ultrarunners to come.\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"beneficial conditions\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3321}, {\"ngram\": \"optimized nutrition\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3342}, {\"ngram\": \"mental preparation\", \"from\": 3344, \"to\": 3362}, {\"ngram\": \"high-performing gear\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3387}, {\"ngram\": \"her mission\", \"from\": 3407, \"to\": 3418}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3420}, {\"ngram\": \"Herron\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s reason\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3459}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s record\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3490}, {\"ngram\": \"the support\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3519}, {\"ngram\": \"the future ultrarunners\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She knows it is possible, and after her most recent accomplishments, she has others putting belief in her vision, too.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI am grateful and honored I could do it and raise the bar on what's possible,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Herron said.\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her most recent accomplishments\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3656}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 3666, \"to\": 3672}, {\"ngram\": \"belief\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3687}, {\"ngram\": \"her vision\", \"from\": 3691, \"to\": 3701}, {\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3769}, {\"ngram\": \"Herron\", \"from\": 3793, \"to\": 3799}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI hope what I did helps increase the interest and participation in ultrarunning and also create more multi-day experiences.\", \"from\": 3807, \"to\": 3933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the interest\", \"from\": 3843, \"to\": 3855}, {\"ngram\": \"participation\", \"from\": 3860, \"to\": 3873}, {\"ngram\": \"more mu